1
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:55,090
Qingshu.

2
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:59,120
Why do you know my Aunt Qin?

3
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:01,520
You followed me here.

4
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:03,180
What exactly is your purpose?

5
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,720
So,

6
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:07,880
you have never trusted me.

7
00:01:07,880 --> 00:01:09,240
I only trust myself.

8
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:15,800
Fine.

9
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:19,480
This jade

10
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:22,890
is a token of the Xiao and Yan families.

11
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:25,440
The Duke and the Marquis of Zhenbei

12
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:27,170
were never political enemies,

13
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:29,900
but brothers through life and death.

14
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:39,180
Many years ago,

15
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:41,240
your father and mine

16
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:43,970
were both trusted ministers of the late Emperor.

17
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:45,680
And the Prince of Ling always saw them

18
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,520
as a thorn in his side.

19
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,800
When the late Emperor was in power,

20
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:53,800
the Prince of Ling privately forged weapons and colluded with the Northern Di,

21
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:56,520
wanting to borrow troops to purge the Emperor's side.

22
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:58,080
And my father held heavy military power.

23
00:01:58,080 --> 00:01:59,120
If the Prince of Ling rebelled,

24
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,520
he had to eliminate him first.

25
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,480
Because of this,

26
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,800
my father and your father

27
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,330
had to pretend to be rivals.

28
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:06,480
In fact,

29
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,979
it was to protect your Yan family.

30
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,480
As for Lady Qin,

31
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:15,600
your mother, my mother and she

32
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,720
were sworn sisters.

33
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:20,880
As for why I followed you,

34
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:22,170
I saw you go out alone

35
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:24,600
and was afraid you would encounter danger on the way,

36
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:26,200
so I secretly protected you.

37
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:30,200
Sworn sisters?

38
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,260
Brothers through life and death?

39
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:36,040
Why have I never heard of this?

40
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:39,240
Why has everyone in the Yan family

41
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:41,370
never mentioned your Xiao family?

42
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:51,520
This letter,

43
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:54,620
I should have given it to you long ago.

44
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:11,360
To the Duke.

45
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:15,840
Heading to the northern border, the cavalry surges like a tide.

46
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:20,320
But how could the sons of the Xiao family fear the neighing horses and howling winds?

47
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,760
If that day ever comes,

48
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:24,050
when this broken jade is reunited,

49
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:27,720
I ask Brother Yan to preside over Jingyan and Qingshu's wedding.

50
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:30,360
If heaven has mercy and I return,

51
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:33,180
I will drink with Brother Yan for three days.

52
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:35,000
If I die in battle,

53
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:37,280
you know I love strong liquor.

54
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:40,460
Please pour three jars of Shaochun wine before my tomb.

55
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:42,400
My son and Qingshu

56
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:44,400
have been engaged since childhood.

57
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:47,640
However, I do not wish to force them with a father's order.

58
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:50,280
If their hearts match when she comes of age,

59
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:52,000
half of the jade will serve as a token.

60
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,530
If they find joy elsewhere,

61
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,520
let it just be a good deed done.

62
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:59,040
Though the jade is broken, it reflects the sun and moon.

63
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:02,160
Brother Yan, you must know my sincere heart.

64
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:04,840
The harsh wind and frost of the northern border

65
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:07,560
are nothing compared to your warm and loyal heart.

66
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,320
I entrust this promise to you.

67
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:18,570
Then this jade pendant guarded with life,

68
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:23,280
what secret is it hiding?

69
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,730
Three years ago,

70
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,360
our fathers

71
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:33,380
discovered a massive vein of ore in Heishui Valley.

72
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,640
To prevent the unexpected,

73
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,300
they forged the map of the vein

74
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,080
into this jade pendant.

75
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,159
Which is exactly

76
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:45,610
the Heishui Valley iron mine map King Ling dreams of.

77
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,540
Your Highness.

78
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,640
Xie Yuheng has met with the Empress Dowager in secret.

79
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:09,000
She ordered him to secretly monitor

80
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,440
the cave where Prince Ling is.

81
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:12,520
Your Highness's move to watch the tigers fight from a safe distance

82
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,560
is truly brilliant.

83
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:16,360
Xie Yuheng and the Empress Dowager are birds of a feather.

84
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:17,960
Now that he has nowhere to go,

85
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:20,560
relying on her is his only chance of survival.

86
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,360
He is now like a stray dog,

87
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:25,920
and this is when he is most likely to expose his flaws.

88
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,650
Send someone

89
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:28,220
to shadow him closely.

90
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,700
Everything he sees

91
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:30,960
must be recorded in detail.

92
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:32,080
Understood.

93
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,400
There is an iron mine in the suburbs of the capital.

94
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:36,159
It seems to have some unusual activities lately.

95
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:36,960
I will go there personally.

96
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,420
That place is a lion's den.

97
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,360
Let Mo Yu accompany you.

98
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:40,920
No need.

99
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:41,960
I'll go with you.

100
00:05:58,760 --> 00:05:59,360
This way.

101
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:02,760
The goods in my cave

102
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:04,080
are all top-notch.

103
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:06,620
Everyone who bought them says they're fine.

104
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,760
This young lady's hands are so white and tender,

105
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:15,000
they don't look like they've touched an abacus

106
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,640
or counted copper coins.

107
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:19,400
My wife only checks the general ledger.

108
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:21,560
Why would she need to handle trivial silver?

109
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,920
The goods in my cave

110
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,280
are not cheap.

111
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:26,720
Have you two prepared enough silver?

112
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:28,880
Naturally.

113
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,100
Straightforward.

114
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,100
Mine owner,

115
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:33,450
more merchants are here to buy ore.

116
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,480
The goods are inside.

117
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,280
Go in and take a look yourselves.

118
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:04,320
What's wrong?

119
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,850
Don't be afraid.

120
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,200
This signal,

121
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:23,160
is the fatal code used by the Xiao Army to transmit news of death.

122
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,400
Could it be that among the miners,

123
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:27,000
there are surviving soldiers of the Xiao Army?

124
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,460
Who are you?

125
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:09,100
How do you know the secret codes of our Zhenbei Army?

126
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:10,920
Zhenbei Army?

127
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:15,480
I am the heir of the Marquis of Zhenbei,

128
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,280
Xiao Jingyan.

129
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:19,000
Your Highness.

130
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:23,100
I am Wang Zhong, a centurion of the Zhenbei Army.

131
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:26,540
The brand on your face,

132
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:27,780
what happened?

133
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,290
Three years ago,

134
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,680
Prince Ling sent a batch of

135
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,409
weapons wrapped in tarpaulin.

136
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:37,940
When the Marquis drew the sword for inspection,

137
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,610
it was as light as a reed.

138
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:42,360
The dark iron was mixed with crushed straw.

139
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:46,540
Even the blood grooves were full of honeycomb-like holes.

140
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,960
The Zhenbei Army suffered a crushing defeat against the Northern Di.

141
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:51,240
The few remaining soldiers returned home,

142
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:53,000
only to be falsely accused of treason

143
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,530
and branded with this mark.

144
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,360
Hear my order, Zhenbei Army!

145
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:07,240
You must all survive.

146
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:11,880
I will have you stand in the Hall of Supreme Harmony,

147
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:16,530
facing all the civil and military officials,

148
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:19,280
to proclaim Cui Tingru's sins

149
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:22,120
to the whole world.

150
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:23,770
Yes, my lord.

151
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,080
Xiao Jingyan,

152
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:36,120
are you still hiding something from me?

153
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:51,160
Your mother was skilled in qin, chess, calligraphy, and painting.

154
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:52,920
My mother was good at singing and dancing.

155
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:54,980
Madam Qin was a kind-hearted healer.

156
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,760
The joy they shared when the three of them gathered

157
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:02,220
sometimes even surpassed the time spent with their husbands.

158
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:06,560
And the place they most often spent their peaceful time together

159
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:07,800
was this teahouse.

160
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:10,600
Seven years ago,

161
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:13,720
your mother solemnly entrusted you

162
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:15,840
to this place.

163
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,440
Qingshu has a fierce temper.

164
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:21,140
If she ever causes trouble in the future,

165
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:23,080
make sure Jingyan protects her.

166
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:25,400
I made Jingyan swear a military pledge

167
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:26,480
that for his entire life,

168
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,680
he must protect Qingshu at all costs.

169
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,760
I once swore before my mother

170
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:37,080
to protect you all my life

171
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,570
and grant you peace.

172
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:42,560
You knew early on about our engagement.

173
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:44,290
Why didn't you come to propose?

174
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,650
Guarding the border for ten years,

175
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:49,240
life and death on the battlefield are unpredictable.

176
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,300
If I died in battle,

177
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:51,740
and you married me,

178
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:53,600
I'm afraid

179
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,520
for the rest of your life,

180
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:58,400
you'd only have a lonely lamp and long nights for company.

181
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,640
That was your wish.

182
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:00,800
Did you ever ask

183
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:01,920
what my wish was?

184
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:06,400
Did I hit your wound?

185
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:08,440
Let me see.

186
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:09,640
I'm fine.

187
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:12,680
Actually,

188
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:16,880
it does hurt a little.

189
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,330
You lied to me again.

190
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:36,320
I was wrong.

191
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:44,120
If you ever hide anything from me again,

192
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,740
I will not forgive you easily.

193
00:11:57,160 --> 00:11:58,640
At a time like this,

194
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:01,500
how can you still be in the mood to do your makeup?

195
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:02,520
Right now,

196
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:04,640
that young Master Xie is a public enemy,

197
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:05,720
hated by everyone.

198
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:08,160
Are you really going to stay chaste for him?

199
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:10,720
You need to plan well for your future.

200
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:13,360
You must not waste your youth.

201
00:12:13,560 --> 00:12:15,200
The emperor is not worried,

202
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,930
but the eunuch is anxious to death.

203
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,480
What are you talking about?

204
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:21,540
I am just doing this for your own good.

205
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:22,960
Right now,

206
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:25,520
I am in charge of the Duke's estate.

207
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:26,920
If you want to marry well,

208
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:29,540
I have my ways to arrange everything for you.

209
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,800
I will definitely find you a desirable husband.

210
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:32,560
In the future,

211
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:34,420
spending day and night together,

212
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:36,080
it will be much more pleasant, won't it?

213
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:37,320
Right now, I have

214
00:12:37,920 --> 00:12:39,840
something more important than getting married.

215
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:40,960
What else

216
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:43,940
could be more important than your marriage?

217
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,080
For this matter,

218
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:48,840
I still need your help, Mother.

219
00:13:14,920 --> 00:13:15,840
Cuimei.

220
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:17,680
Yong.

221
00:13:18,760 --> 00:13:19,480
Huachao.

222
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,410
Weikun Huachao.

223
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,720
Longcong Biaohao.

224
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:27,100
Shuangbin.

225
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,080
Shuangbin.

226
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:28,680
Ningzheng.

227
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:29,340
Ningzheng.

228
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:32,560
Haochun Kangshuaihua.

229
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:37,320
Weichao.

230
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,400
Qiangyuan Liangbo.

231
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:55,280
Xi.

232
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:57,680
Taoqiang Xi.

233
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:58,600
Taoqiang.

234
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:04,080
Huiyue Yunqing.

235
00:14:07,160 --> 00:14:07,680
Yiyi.

236
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:08,280
Yiyi.
